Output demos/hoogle.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 70ms
Set Width 1500
Set Height 850

Hide
Type "ghcitty"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Ctrl+l
Sleep 500ms
Show

# Hoogle search
Type ":hoogle layoutz"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Doc lookup
Type ":doc sort"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Sleep 1s
